-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/spanish-wealth-tax-to-raise-1-billion-euros-pais-says.html
The wealth tax that  Spain ’s
government plans to re-introduce tomorrow will affect 150,000
people and raise 1 billion euros, El Pais reported, citing
Public Works Minister Jose Blanco, who is also the government’s
